# Purple Club Development Rules

## Tech Stack
- Framework: Next.js (App Router)
- Styling: Tailwind CSS (Strictly match colors from purplebitcoin.com)
- Web3: Solana Wallet Adapter + @solana/web3.js
- State: Token-gate access based on 1 PBTC (Mint: HfMbPyDdZH6QMaDDUokjYCkHxzjoGBMpgaUvpLWGbF5p)

## UI/UX Standards
- Theme: "The Vault" (Dark, Premium, High-Contrast Purple/Gold).
- Mobile-First: The "Membership Pass" must be perfectly legible on a phone screen in high-glare environments (like a storefront).
- Privacy: Never store user wallet data on a server. Everything is client-side verification.

## Implementation Goal
- Build a Progressive Web App (PWA) that feels like a native "Members Only" club.
- Use a central `merchants.ts` configuration to drive the directory UI.